OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FThe early summer heatwave that struck
OL,7,Fmuch of Europe in June has been linked
OL,8,Fto over 14,000 deaths.
OL,10,FThe EuroMOMO mortality monitoring hub,
OL,11,Fwhich receives data from two dozen
OL,12,Fcountries, gave an estimate of 14,260
OL,13,Ffor excess mortality from all causes
OL,14,Fin the week ending June 28, more than
OL,15,F12,000 of those deaths being among
OL,16,Fpeople age 65 and older.
OL,18,FThat's out of a total 84,583 deaths
OL,19,Fthat week, figures in the preceding
OL,20,Fand following weeks were far lower.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
