PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784400496
OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FLasse Vestergaard of Denmark's Statens
OL,7,FSerum Institut, which coordinates
OL,8,FEuroMOMO, said that "we attribute this
OL,9,Fto the heatwave affecting quite a lot
OL,10,Fof countries in Europe, and we do that
OL,11,Fbecause there is no other obvious
OL,12,Fexplanation that could explain such a
OL,13,Fhigh excess mortality happening at the
OL,14,Fmoment."
OL,16,FSuch a high excess in a single week is
OL,17,F"highly unusual," he added.
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@HO]yD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
