OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FOf those deaths, it says that about
OL,7,F550 occurred in late May and about
OL,8,F2,200 in late June.
OL,10,FThis year brought national heat
OL,11,Frecords for May of 35.1C and for June
OL,12,Fof more than 37C.
OL,14,FLess than a month later, the UK is in
OL,15,Fanother heatwave, which has seen
OL,16,Ftemperatures above 30C recorded for 12
OL,17,Fdays in a row.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
