OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FGermany's disease control centre, the
OL,7,FRobert Koch Institute, directly
OL,8,Fattributed 6,830 deaths to heat this
OL,9,Fyear through early July, 6,470 of them
OL,10,Famong people 65 and older.
OL,12,FTemperatures in Germany late last
OL,13,Fmonth hit their highest levels since
OL,14,Frecords began, peaking with a
OL,15,Fmeasurement of 41.7C on June 28,
OL,16,Faccording to the German Weather
OL,17,FService.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
