OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FAn estimated 937 deaths in Spain in
OL,7,FJune were attributed to excess heat,
OL,8,Faccording to the Carlos III Health
OL,9,FInstitute, an official Spanish
OL,10,Fmonitoring agency.
OL,12,FLast month was Spain's second-hottest
OL,13,FJune on record, with temperatures 3.2C
OL,14,Fabove the monthly normal average,
OL,15,Faccording to the AEMET weather agency.
OL,17,FA five-day heat wave saw temperatures
OL,18,Fregularly surpass 40C, AEMET said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
