OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn Belgium, there were 1,747 deaths
OL,12,Fabove what would usually be expected
OL,13,Fduring the heatwave that ran from June
OL,14,F18 to July 1, according to Sciensano,
OL,15,Fthe country's public health institute.
OL,17,FAn initial estimate of excess death
OL,18,Ffigures from the June heat wave found
OL,19,Fthat the Netherlands had 480 more
OL,20,Fdeaths than expected, according to its
OL,21,Fpublic health service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
