OL,3,CEarly summer heatwave in Europe linked
OL,4,Cto more than 14,000 deaths
OL,6,FIncreased mortality was particularly
OL,7,Fnotable in eastern and southern areas,
OL,8,Fwhere the temperatures were the
OL,9,Fhighest.
OL,11,FThe country saw its highest
OL,12,Ftemperature ever for June, with the
OL,13,FDutch weather service registering
OL,14,F36.8C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
